    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD model provides High assurance for the CPB hemolysis COU. Seven of thirteen factors were formally assessed, with six accepted at Gradation 1 under MRL 2 scoping. The team judges that the overall body of evidence supports a High assurance designation based on the strength of validation agreement and established software QA. The discretization error factor shortfall (achieved Gradation 1 versus required Gradation 3) is noted but considered acceptable given the qualitative mesh sensitivity argument from analogous published studies.",
